description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Power Yoga Flow' from the channel Owen Henn.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Nature Flow vibe.
The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release. The The Nature Flow vibe means Breath-centered, full-body, outdoor rhythm. This is especially good for When you want fresh air, nature, and full-body movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Start slow and build up with Owen during this power flow from a snowy morning in New Hampshire. *Yoga blocks optional. ...
